title: Gavin Harrison & 05ric - The Man Who Sold Himself
description:
This is the new album from Gavin Harisson (from Porcupine Tree) and 05ric. A lovely, avantgarde CD which brings to mind the old King Crimson's albums.

Gavin Harrison - a Porcupine Tree drummer and one of the best drum players. 05Ric - a real jazz guitar virtuoso.

I'm uploading since there is no other torrent for this. Download this and if you like - buy the album!
